---
title: Poppin’ Jalapeño Beef Stuffed Peppers with Cheddar & Sour Cream
description: A comfort food classic, these stuffed peppers get a kick from our bold Southwest spice blend and quick-pickled jalapeños. Bell peppers are stuffed with a creamy rice and pork filling, then smothered with cheddar cheese and baked until browned and bubbling. A final dollop of sour cream is all that’s needed for these crowd-pleasing favorites.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/666862f6223895220f19805c-083720a5.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6669e554223895220f198d09-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
